    {
      "id": "009",
      "title": "in / on / at 時間 — 看時間長短挑",
      "emoji": "🕐",
      "category": "介系詞",
      "level": "G6",
      "rule": "用「時間長短」記最直覺:\n🟢 AT (最小) → 一個時刻 / 鐘點:at 8 o'clock、at noon、at midnight、at lunchtime\n🟡 ON (中) → 一整天:on Monday、on July 5、on Christmas Day、on a rainy day\n🔴 IN (最大) → 月、年、季節、長段時間:in May、in 2026、in summer、in the morning\n口訣:時間越大,介系詞越大(at < on < in)。",
      "examples": [
        {
          "en": "We have class at 9 a.m.",
          "zh": "我們九點上課。(精確時刻 → at)"
        },
        {
          "en": "My birthday is on July 5th.",
          "zh": "我的生日是 7 月 5 日。(某天 → on)"
        },
        {
          "en": "It is hot in summer.",
          "zh": "夏天很熱。(整個季節 → in)"
        },
        {
          "en": "I read in the morning.",
          "zh": "我在早上看書。(早上 = 一段時間 → in)"
        },
        {
          "en": "But: I sleep at night.",
          "zh": "但:我晚上睡覺。(at night 是例外!要硬背)"
        }
      ],
      "quiz": [
        {
          "q": "I get up ___ 7 o'clock.",
          "options": [
            "in",
            "on",
            "at"
          ],
          "answer": 2
        },
        {
          "q": "We have a party ___ Sunday.",
          "options": [
            "in",
            "on",
            "at"
          ],
          "answer": 1
        },
        {
          "q": "She was born ___ January.",
          "options": [
            "in",
            "on",
            "at"
          ],
          "answer": 0
        },
        {
          "q": "The stars come out ___ night.",
          "options": [
            "in",
            "on",
            "at"
          ],
          "answer": 2
        },
        {
          "q": "School starts ___ September.",
          "options": [
            "in",
            "on",
            "at"
          ],
          "answer": 0
        }
      ]
    },
